  <text>
    <style color="0xaaaaaa">(Crushed ore is an intermediary product in the processing of ores, see the ore processing tab in JEI/REI/EMI for any ore's specific processing steps)</style>
  </text>
  <br></br>
  <text>Crushed ore is obtained from either <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/macerator" underlined="true">macerating</style> or <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/forge_hammer" underlined="true">forge hammering</style> <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/raw" underlined="true">Raw Ore</style>, with the forge hammer giving a 1:1 ratio, and the macerator ~1:2 ratio which gets better with higher tier macerators.</text>
